description:
Today we invite Scar to check out my newly built storage room featuring a handy shulker swapping organization system. We use our moss factory to power a new bonemeal bamboo farm.

Then we head over to the Frogger game to do some testing with Cubfan and Bdubs, and focus on fine-tuning the game mechanics for it.
